dc_description_s: This data layer represents land use for Vilas County, Wisconsin in 2017. It is a feature class within the geodatabase NVilas_LandUse_2017.gdbN. [The proposed land use classification identified during community planning activities and sometimes defined at the parcel level, but typically proposed land use units are larger than the parcel.]
dct_provenance_s: Arthur H. Robinson Map Library - University of Wisconsin
dc_creator_sm: Vilas County Land Information and Mapping Department
